      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/private-hospital-owner-prospect-medical-files-for-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Prospect Medical Holdings Inc.曾经是资金短缺的医院的积极买家，但由于债务堆积和成本飙升而申请破产。]]></description>
