      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/em-currencies-are-at-central-banks-mercy-as-fiscal-policy-lags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场央行正在成为保护当地货币免受投机性攻击和财政赤字冲击的第一道防线。]]></description>
